            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>cornflour</strong>, <strong>soy sauce </strong>and <strong>sesame oil </strong>in a bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>stir-fry sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-5-1647946610966-x200.jpg",
