            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked through, add the <strong>basmati rice</strong>, <strong>chopped wilted spinach </strong>and <strong>drained sweetcorn </strong>to the pan</p><p>Pour in the <strong>stir-fry sauce</strong>, give it a stir<strong> </strong>and then cook for 2-3 min or until everything is warmed through and coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>Chinese-style chicken & sweetcorn stir-fry</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
